Whoops, forgot about EndBringer.

::EndBringer::

EndBringer ignores the shots digging into his armor, firing two more 
missiles at the Trainer base.



--- In nbwrpg@y..., Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> Oh good. Scyther is a flyer :-)
> 
> ::Scyther/Incarcinator/Demise::
> 
> Scyther flies back a bit more, deciding that this was a safe enough 
> distance. He then aims his charge launcher at Hellpeon and fires 
four 
> charges.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> Incarcinator continues to fly up, dodging several blasts and firing 
a 
> shot at the Trainer base (very fast, explosive shell). His gaining 
> altitude allowed him to see most shots and dodge them before they 
got 
> close. Aiming at Hellpeon, Incarcinator fires two more shells at 
him.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> Demise continues to run, several autogun blasts denting the armor 
on 
> his back. He jumps behind a hill for cover, wishing that someone 
> would exit the ship so that he could tear them apart.
> 
> 
> 
> --- In nbwrpg@y..., "CYBERWOLF4" <cyberwolf4@p...> wrote:
> > They'd be able to detect footprints in the sand unless he's 
flying 
> but
> > they'd only be able to guess where he'd be.
